-> When user clicks on start button then startOrstop function will be called.
-> From there start function willbe called, it will invoke startService function and will pass the intent with the current time
-> After that onStartCommand function of the StopWatchService class will get triggered.
-> That function will invoke inner class stopWatchTimerTask
-> Inside the class current time will be incresed by 1 second
-> Now that new time will be recieved by BroadcastReceiver and displayed in the text view